name: 新手引导步骤1
info_en: Hi, welcome to the magic garden? Please follow me!
info_cn: 你好，第一次来到魔法花园？请跟我来！

name: 新手引导步骤2
info_en: This is your own garden, let's sow the Clover.
info_cn: 这里是花地，让我们撒下四叶草的种子。

name: 新手引导步骤3
info_en: Now, you can water for the Clover seed and speed it up.
info_cn: 现在为四叶草浇水，助它生长。

name: 新手引导步骤4
info_en: Tap to collect coins and keep it growing.
info_cn: 点击收获金币，进行下一阶段成长。

name: 新手引导步骤5
info_en: Oh, the Clover is ripe! You can summon a new piece of suit.
info_cn: 哇！四叶草成熟啦！用仙子的能量召唤它吧！

name: 新手引导步骤6
info_en: Congratulations, you get a new clothes.
info_cn: 恭喜你获得了新的服饰！

name: 新手引导步骤7
info_en: Now dress up the fairy with new clothes.
info_cn: 现在就装扮上刚刚获得的服饰吧！

name: 完成引导
info_en: Guide completed! Start your journey in the magic world!
info_cn: 完成引导！欢迎来到魔法花园的世界！

name: 金币召唤引导
info_en: You can use coins or gems to summon the clothes, and they have different successful rate.
info_cn: 有两种召唤方式，金币召唤和钻石召唤，它们的成功率不一样哦！

name: 金币召唤引导
info_en: Watch the video to reduce the plant time.
info_cn: 观看视频可以减少种植时间哦！

name: 除草引导
info_en: Oh，the flower was grown with weeds. Use the herbicides for removing it now! If you don't use herbicides, the probablity of getting clothes will reduce by 5%.
info_cn: 哎呀，花田里长了杂草，快用灭草剂吧 ！如果没有除草的话，会降低5%的衣服召唤成功率哦

name: 除虫引导
info_en: Oh, the flower was grown with pests. Use the insecticide for killing them now! If you don't use insecticide, the probablity of getting clothes will reduce by 5%.
info_cn: 哎呀，花田里有虫子了，快用除虫剂吧 如果没有除虫的话，会降低5%的衣服召唤成功率哦
